      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities must cover the full VAD operating envelope and device geometry without extrapolation beyond validated parameter space.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic pump geometry; patient-specific impeller geometry differences introduce extrapolation. Two of five VAD operating points lie outside validated flow-speed envelope. Achieved level 3 vs required 5."
    },
